Meet Kaylene

Meet Kaylene! She has been a part of Halcyon on and off for the past 4 years! She’s currently working as a pre-kindergarten teaching assistant and absolutely loves the music we sing in Halcyon!

Like all Halcyonites, she loves singing the Messiah at Christmas time. She describes the choir as inspiring and loves the challenge that comes with working with so many talented and wonderful people!
